.env
.env.local
# chroma_db/ is deliberately NOT ignored — the prebuilt index must ship inside
# the image. The free tier has no persistent disk and only 512MB RAM, so without
# it the container re-embeds 1,232 docs on every cold start and OOMs before it
# can bind a port. Rebuild with: python -m app.rag.ingestion --reset
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
venv/
.git/
